WACList
Worksheet.Query: [$PriceListSelect], CASE WHEN mn_struct_line_item_ver.start_date < [$PeriodStart] THEN (select date_dim_id from mn_date_dim where date_num=[$PeriodStartDim]) ELSE (select date_dim_id from mn_date_dim where date_num=to_char(mn_struct_line_item_ver.start_date, 'yyyyMMdd')) END as start_date, CASE WHEN mn_struct_line_item_ver.end_date > [$PeriodEnd] THEN (select date_dim_id from mn_date_dim where date_num=[$PeriodEndDim]) ELSE (select date_dim_id from mn_date_dim where date_num=to_char(mn_struct_line_item_ver.end_date, 'yyyyMMdd')) END as end_date [$PriceListFrom] AND mn_struct_line_item_ver.start_date <= [$PeriodEnd] AND mn_struct_line_item_ver.end_date >= [$PeriodStart] ) [$PriceListWhere] AND sdv.struct_doc_type = [$PriceListType] AND mn_struct_line_item_ver.start_date <= [$PeriodEnd] AND mn_struct_line_item_ver.end_date >= [$PeriodStart]

Worksheet.name: ProductFilter
Worksheet.Query: select distinct itm.item_id from mn_item_ver itm where itm.item_id in ([SQ:ProductFilter:]) AND itm.ver_start_date < [$DataCutoff] AND itm.ver_end_date >= [$DataCutoff] AND [RC:MapItem:itm]

Worksheet.name: NDC11SetActive
Worksheet.Query: [$NDC11SetAMPProdSetSelect] '3.AMP.ACTIVE' as status [$NDC11SetAMPProdSetFrom] AND ( base11.shelf_life_exp_date is null OR base11.shelf_life_exp_date >= [$PeriodStart] ) AND ( base11.divestiture_date is null OR base11.divestiture_date >= [$PeriodStart] ) AND ( [$ProductLife] >= [$OneCalcPeriod] OR ( [$ProductLife] < [$OneCalcPeriod] AND base11.acquisition_date is null ) )

Worksheet.name: NDC11SetTransferred
Worksheet.Query: [$NDC11SetAMPProdSetSelect] '2.AMP.TRANSFERRED' as status [$NDC11SetAMPProdSetFrom] AND ( base11.shelf_life_exp_date is null OR base11.shelf_life_exp_date >= [$PeriodStart] ) AND ( base11.divestiture_date is null OR base11.divestiture_date >= [$PeriodStart] ) /* product acquired with product life between 0 and 1 month */ AND ( [$ProductLife] < [$OneCalcPeriod] AND base11.acquisition_date is not null )

Worksheet.name: NDC11SetExpired
Worksheet.Query: [$NDC11SetAMPProdSetSelect] '4.AMP.TERMINATED' AS status [$NDC11SetAMPProdSetFrom] AND ( base11.shelf_life_exp_date >= ADD_MONTHS([$PeriodStart], -12) ) AND (base11.shelf_life_exp_date < [$PeriodStart])

Worksheet.name: NotReportedNDC11s
Worksheet.Query: select base11.item_id as ndc11_id, me11to9.dest_id as ndc9_id, base11.medicaid_units_per_pack as medicaid_upp from mn_item_ver base11 inner join mn_map_edge_ver me11to9 on ( base11.item_id = me11to9.source_id AND me11to9.edge_type = 1 /* PART_OF */ AND me11to9.ver_start_date < [$DataCutoff] AND me11to9.ver_end_date >= [$DataCutoff] ) where base11.ver_start_date < [$DataCutoff] AND base11.ver_end_date >= [$DataCutoff] AND [RC:MapItem:base11]
